  "question": "为什么非洲草原的食草动物不预防性地杀死有攻击预谋的食肉捕猎者？",
  "author": "山高县",
  "content": "<p>光见狮子吃肉，不见狮子挨揍。其实食草动物在有机会时攻击食肉动物，远比食肉动物的捕猎要坚决的多。</p><p>非洲象，水牛和河马的攻击性比狮子高不是一点半点。别忘了，食草动物不怎么怕受伤。。。。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-64e884913e8dd0ac306820af26055e0f_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2276\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-09011881ade48a0c1a6b267dcd6b3044_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2276\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-64e884913e8dd0ac306820af26055e0f_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;2276&#39; height=&#39;1280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"2276\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-09011881ade48a0c1a6b267dcd6b3044_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2276\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-64e884913e8dd0ac306820af26055e0f_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-64e884913e8dd0ac306820af26055e0f_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>水牛群列阵攻击狮群</figcaption></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d52bd465c35f1f3b6750afc63bce9c81_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"2276\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-854ceab65f0904f50b761cb8c4c5f83c_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2276\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d52bd465c35f1f3b6750afc63bce9c81_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;2276&#39; height=&#39;1280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"2276\" data-rawheight=\"1280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-854ceab65f0904f50b761cb8c4c5f83c_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\